narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 110 05 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 110 05 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: Great course. Prof. Williams is knowledgeable, but still quite laid back. The assignments build upon each other nicely. Excellent, wide-ranging syllabus.
I would absolutely recommend this class to another student!
Definitely recommend--especially if at all interested in East Asian culture.
Definitely take this course- very interesting material presented in a more laid-back discussion atmosphere.
